## Third-Party Notices

### City of Doors — Map Data (CC BY 4.0)
https://github.com/amargon/city-of-doors

The map dataset (location data, coordinates, venue descriptions) bundled in this
module originates from the "City of Doors" project by amargon. The map data is
licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The underlying source code of the City of Doors project is licensed under the
MIT License. Copyright (c) 2017 amargon.

Modifications made in this project:
- Map location data (map.json) is transformed at runtime into FoundryVTT
  JournalEntry and Scene Note documents. The source data content is unmodified.
- The Sigil map image (sigil-map.png) is used unmodified as a Scene background.

### City of Doors — Artwork Credits

The Sigil map artwork is derived from the planewalker.com community resources.

  Montage: Denis "Ambrus" Richard
  Original cartography: Rob Lazzaretti
  Additional artwork: Tony DiTerlizzi & David S. "Diesel" LaForce

